Parameters.Name: pMode
Parameters.Prompt: 1 - New Live Version, 2 - Remove a live version, 3 - Remove a static version, 4 Update Live version with another version, 5 - Take a snapshot, 6 - Create Variances

Parameters.Name: pSrcElement
Parameters.Prompt: With Mode 1 - Select a source version to use as a base for the new version. With modes 2 & 3 select the version you wish to delete, 4 - select version to copy from, 5 - select version to copy from

Parameters.Name: pElement
Parameters.Prompt: With Mode 1 - enter name of new version. With modes 2 & 3 select the version you wish to delete, 4 - version to update, 5 - version to create/update
